      "author": "philpalmieri",
      "description": "Sort and group controls for task lists. A subtle controls bar on every list adds Sort (priority, due date, start date, reference, title) and Group (none, priority, due date, reference) dropdowns. Group headers are small muted labels with counts; 'no priority' and 'no due date' buckets always land last. Selections persist as you navigate, and sorting applies within each group.",
